                p Manchester based mathematician, Dr. Katie Steckles, after finishing her PhD in 2011, has gained a global recognition by choosing to be one of the most influential female mathematics and science communicators in the world. She talks about maths in schools, at science festivals, on BBC radio, at music festivals, as part of theatre shows and on the internet.

