                p Dr. Steckles has appeared in several videos on the YouTube channel Numberphile; is the organiser of the Manchester branch of MathsJam, a monthly pub night which involves fun maths, puzzles and other interesting mathsy things; is the organiser of Manchester Girl Geeks, the Manchester branch of the world famous Girl Geek Dinners.

